latestPosts.caption: My Italian Core memory 💍✨ Despite loosing our luggages at the airport, I can’t imagine how calm Yash was through the whole trip in Italy. And cherry on top, he proposed through all this. I could never🥹. But that’s what completes us right? If I am anxious or nervous, I know he’s there to handle things which I might not able to in that moment. And these photos remind me of that. How we’re there for each other no matter what. No matter what surprises life throws at us, we have to focus on the good side bcz we’ve got each other, & that’s what matters right? ❤️✨ 🥺💍
